  "texts": [
    "Following the program can reduce catastrophizing.",
    "• Less panic • \"For me, what was a real game changer... was also realizing that most people in this condition tend to have the same thoughts; thinking, for example, that there's something perhaps serious hidden behind it, thinking that it will never stop, that you could die from it, and all that.",
    "It was good for me, because these are patterns I really have.",
    "Then, I thought of myself more like a normal person....",
    "The panic I used to feel about my pain has almost completely disappeared, and I realize how much I can change my situation myself.\""
  ],
